Here is guide about the use of this slackchatbot built with Ruby. Please, follow the steps down below, after clone this repository to your machine:
1. Open your terminal;
2. Open the cloned repository;
3. Install 'rvm' - learn how to install correctly here at https://rvm.io/rvm/install ;
4. Install the ruby 2.2.0, type 'rvm install ruby 2.2.0';
5. Type 'gem install bundle';
6. Type 'bundle install';

On slack, add this app - Click on Browse Apps option next the word Apps in the navigationbar -Look for vini and add.

Backing to the terminal use your slack API token with the command SLACK_API_TOKEN=... bundle exec ruby pongbot.rb .Fill the '...' with the token.
